<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Reddit posts consistently rank on the first page of Google search results — a well-crafted, genuinely helpful post in a relevant subreddit can drive referral traffic for months. Combined with creators who already have the audience, the $100 goes toward people and distribution, not ads. <span class="inline-flex" data-state="closed"><a href="https://www.tloproduction.com/post/social-as-a-search-channel-optimizing-for-tiktok-reddit-and-discovery-in-2025" target="_blank" class="group/tag relative h-[18px] rounded-full inline-flex items-center overflow-hidden -translate-y-px cursor-pointer"><span class="relative transition-colors h-full max-w-[180px] overflow-hidden px-1.5 inline-flex items-center font-small rounded-full border-0.5 border-border-300 bg-bg-200 group-hover/tag:bg-accent-900 group-hover/tag:border-accent-100/60"><span class="text-nowrap text-text-300 break-all truncate font-normal group-hover/tag:text-text-200">TLo Productions</span></span><span class="transition-all opacity-[0%] h-[17px] absolute right-[0.5px] rounded-r-full flex items-center px-1.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-900/0 via-accent-900/100 via-30% to-accent-900/100 group-hover/tag:opacity-[100%]"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="transition-all group-hover/tag:ease-out duration-[500ms] ease-in text-accent-100 group-hover/tag:scale-[100%] scale-[80%] group-hover/tag:opacity-[100%] opacity-[0%] -mr-[2px]"><path d="M200,64V168a8,8,0,0,1-16,0V83.31L69.66,197.66a8,8,0,0,1-11.32-11.32L172.69,72H88a8,8,0,0,1,0-16H192A8,8,0,0,1,200,64Z"></path></svg></span></a></span></p>
